============================================================================
PROJECT: MRCA - Advanced Parallel HybridRAG - Intelligent Fusion Technology
============================================================================

This license applies to all documentation, guides, essays, research materials,
and educational content for the MRCA (Mining Regulatory Compliance Assistant) 
project.

The MRCA project documentation covers the implementation and research behind 
novel Advanced Parallel HybridRAG technology that performs simultaneous 
VectorRAG and GraphRAG execution with intelligent context fusion for enhanced 
mining regulatory compliance assistance.

Project Type: Capstone Research Project
Technology: Advanced Parallel HybridRAG - Intelligent Fusion System
Domain: Mining Safety and Regulatory Compliance + AI Research

